    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Combining the best of the Fortress and Pavise shields, the Tower shield is a rare item to find - only master craftsmen could build one balanced enough to account for a perfect defense.</p><p>As rare as it is, it is also very expensive, costing more than the two others combined.</p><p><strong>Special. </strong>Cover(3/4). As an action you can stand your ground as a protective element for everything behind the shield. You create a protection area of a line of 15ft. behind the shield, which provide a certain level of cover. This effect also works for spell attacks that have an area of effect of a line or cone.<hr /><p>Wielding the <i>Tower</i> provides a +4 bonus to your Armor Class. You can only benefit from only one shield at a time.</p><p><strong>Note.</strong> As a protector shield, the wielder must have a Strength ability score of 13 or higher and imposes disadvantage on Dexterity (Stealth) checks.</p>",
